<https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs.ttl> a ftr:Metric, dqv:Metric, dcat:Resource ;
    dcterms:identifier "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs.ttl"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs.ttl"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    dcat:landingPage "https://ostrails.github.io/assessment-component-metadata-records/metric/FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs.ttl"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    dcterms:title "FAIR Metric - I3 - Metadata - Database references related databases"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:label "FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "FM_I3_FS_RelatedDBs"^^xsd:string ;
    dcterms:description """**What is being measured?**

This metric evaluates whether the database references related databases. In FAIRsharing, this corresponds to the FAIRsharing database record containing at least one **shares_data_with** or **related_to** relationship linking it to another FAIRsharing database record. Expected input is the DOI or URL of the registry (e.g. FAIRsharing) record under evaluation.

**Why should we measure it?**

I3 requires that (meta)data include qualified references to other (meta)data. Within the FAIRsharing interpretation of this principle for database-level FAIR evaluation, explicit relationships among databases represent the traditional interpretation of qualified references. This metric uses the relationships provided within FAIRsharing database records to determine whether the database explicitly references other databases. Relationships among databases are important FAIR-enabling characteristics because they provide machine-readable connections between related resources and support the broader ecosystem of relationships and interoperability represented by FAIR Principle I3."""^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:keyword "FAIR"^^xsd:string ;
    schema:about "Not applicable"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:applicationArea <http://www.fairsharing.org/ontology/subject/SRAO_0000401> ;
    ftr:inDimension <https://w3id.org/fair/principles/terms/I3> ;
    dcat:version "1.0.0"^^xsd:string ;
    
    
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
     
    
    
    
    
    ftr:supportedBy <https://tools.ostrails.eu/champion>; 
    
